<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Your Job Match | Jobalytics&trade;</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9gVQ4dYFwwWSjIDZnLEWnxCjeSWFphJiwGPXr1jddIhOegiu1FwO5qRGvFXOdJZ4" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        .fade-in-down {
            animation: fade-in-down 2s ease infinite;
            animation-iteration-count: 1;
        }
        
        @keyframes fade-in-down {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .hvr-float {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            -webkit-transform: perspective(1px) translateZ(0);
            transform: perspective(1px) translateZ(0);
            box-shadow: 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
            -webkit-transition-duration: 0.3s;
            transition-duration: 0.3s;
            -webkit-transition-property: transform;
            transition-property: transform;
            -webkit-transition-timing-function: ease-out;
            transition-timing-function: ease-out;
        }
        
        .hvr-float:hover,
        .hvr-float:focus,
        .hvr-float:active {
            -webkit-transform: translateY(-8px);
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: Roboto;
            background: -webkit-linear-gradient(90deg, #2BC0E4 10%, #EAECC6 90%);
            /* Chrome 10+, Saf5.1+ */
            background: -moz-linear-gradient(90deg, #2BC0E4 10%, #EAECC6 90%);
            /* FF3.6+ */
            background: -ms-linear-gradient(90deg, #2BC0E4 10%, #EAECC6 90%);
            /* IE10 */
            background: -o-linear-gradient(90deg, #2BC0E4 10%, #EAECC6 90%);
            /* Opera 11.10+ */
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2BC0E4 10%, #EAECC6 90%);
            /* W3C */
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        textarea {
            resize: none;
            width: 100%;
            border: 2px solid #BF1F64;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        button {
            color: #fff;
            background: #DD2E64;
            border: none;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-bottom: 4px solid #AE2167;
            transition: all .2s ease;
            outline: none;
        }
        
        #check {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            height: 35px;
            font-size: medium;
        }
        
        #returnbutton {
            margin-top: 5px;
            height: 50px;
            font-size: medium;
        }
        
        #resultsbox {
            margin-top: 5px;
            background-color: lightgrey;
        }
        
        button:hover {
            background: #AE2167;
            color: #fff;
        }
        
        button:active {
            border: 0;
        }
    </style>


</head>

<body>
    <div id="logo" class="text-center">
        <img src="img/Untitled.png" style="display:block; margin-top: 30px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto">
        <h1 class="fade-in-down">Enter your job posting here.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div id="leftcolumn" class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card hvr-float" style="width: 100%;   border: 2px solid #FBB959;
  border-radius:4px;">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="img/interview2.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">Why is this important?</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">You should modify your resume appropriately for each role you apply to. Make sure you list specific, relevant experiences and change your skills or projects accordingly.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="midcolumn" class="col-md-4 fade-in-down">
                <form action="/jobmatch" method="POST">
                    <input type="text" name="joblink" placeholder="Job URL" style="width: 505px;">
                <button >Check my potential match.</button>

                </form>
                
                <textarea readonly id="results" rows="12">
                    <%= returnedmatch %>
                </textarea>


             
                <form action='/home' method="POST">
                    <button id="return">Return</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div id="rightcolumn" class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card hvr-float" style="width: 100%;   border: 2px solid #FBB959;
  border-radius:4px;">
                    <img class="card-img-top" src="img/hired.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4 class="card-title">How does it work?</h4>
                        <p class="card-text">Our algorithms use Indico-supported functions to determine your fit with the provided job description of your choice. Through Wolfram One, we prepare your results visually.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>